# Config YAML

Skill: `.cursor/skills/add-config-item/` (apps/cli/mas) or `.cursor/skills/macos-preference/` (macos.yaml).

- Source of truth for install targets — never duplicate in shell scripts
- Do not hand-edit `Brewfile` — run `make brewfile` after `apps.yaml` / `cli.yaml` changes
- Prefer `./bootstrap.sh --add-app/cli/mas` over manual edits
- After list size changes, update `tests/run_tests.sh` assert counts
- `validation.strict` / `fail_on_warnings` in profiles are not implemented
